article.headline: Knox scores 19, Alabama State knocks off Omaha 85-67
article.description: — Amarr Knox scored 19 points as Alabama State beat Omaha 85-67 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Knox scores 19, Alabama State knocks off Omaha 85-67
article.story: AKRON, Ohio -- — Amarr Knox scored 19 points as Alabama State beat Omaha 85-67 on Friday night. Knox shot 6 of 9 from the field and 5 for 5 from the line for the Hornets (2-2). Micah Simpsom scored 17 points and added six rebounds. Antonio Madlock shot 4 of 8 from the field and 6 for 8 from the line to finish with 15 points. The Mavericks (2-4) were led in scoring by Marquel Sutton, who finished with 22 points and 14 rebounds. Lance Waddles added 11 points and six assists for Omaha. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
